<paragraph base="F45932124" id="IFRS16_BC308"><paranum>BC308</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="BC308"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P2327"><xref base="F47963587" href="IFRS16_TOC.dita#IFRS16_TOC0001" id="IFRS16_X1196">IFRS 16</xref> permits a lessee not to apply the recognition requirements to leases for which the underlying asset is of low value. The IASB&#x2019;s reasons are explained in <xref base="F47963588" href="IFRS16_gBC98-BC104.dita#IFRS16_gBC98-BC104/IFRS16_gBC98-BC104_TI" id="IFRS16_X1197">paragraphs BC98&#x2013;BC104</xref>. The FASB decided not to include such an exemption.</p></body></paragraph>